\c 10 Vakadzi vatorwa vanodzingwa 1 Zvino Ezira akati achinyengetera, achizvireurura, achichema nokuzviwisira pasi pamberi peimba yaMwari, ungano huru-huru yavarume navakadzi navana vavaIsiraeri vakaungana kwaari; nokuti vanhu vakachema zvikuru kwaivo, 2 Ipapo Shekuita mulawakoman~awaJehieri, mumwe wavanakomana vaErami, akapindura, akati kuna Ezira, "Ta‑ katadzira Mwari wedu zvatakawana vaka‑ dzi vatorwa vendudzi dzenyika iyi; kunyange zvakadaro vaIsiraeri vachine
